          "description": "I absolutely love this urgent care!\nI recently went in for blood work that I needed for school, and I had a wonderful experience from start to finish.\nThe medical assistants, Samantha, Cate and Alaijah, were incredible. I was very nervous about getting my blood drawn, but they were so kind, patient, and reassuring that they made the whole process feel easy and stress-free.\nTee at the front desk was amazing as well. She helped me get registered quickly and was friendly, welcoming, and professional throughout the entire process.\nI've also been seen multiple times by the PAs, Kristi and Heather, and they are both outstanding. They always take the time to listen, thoroughly evaluate my concerns, and provide excellent care, all with a smile on their faces. They truly make you feel heard and cared for.\nIt's not often that you find a healthcare team that is consistently compassionate, professional, and efficient. Every person I've interacted with here has gone above and beyond. I highly recommend this urgent care to anyone looking for quality care and a great patient experience!",
