          "description": "MedRite in Tribeca was fantastic. I sliced my finger badly on a broken glass, hopped in a car and headed directly to them. From the moment I arrived, they gave me first class care. I required stitches, after care, stitch removal. The receptionists were pleasant, doctors and assistants brilliant. Dr Heather and Dr. Chrissy were phenomenal, so kind and thorough. I will always go back to MedRite for urgent care now if I need fast, reliable, exceptional care. They are simply the best.",
