          "description": "Everyone was so nice and friendly that it was a really pleasant experience\nNever at Urgent Care have I been treated so well!\nEveryone who works there is so nice and the facility is really clean. However, Kristy is truly special! I have seen her on 3 separate occasions and each time she was so friendly, kind, and demonstrated so much empathy felt so positive about my experience She took her time and seemed really interested in me and my symptoms.\nShe\u2019s also really great to talk to!",
