          "description": "Tyronique made this 5 stars. I really truly hope they recognize how great she is! She was so professional and attentive. And her energy was made me feel like I could be comfortable telling her what I went into urgent care for (it was a lil uncomfortable for me to talk about). She was so speedy with everything that had to get done. But she was so attentive to me too. It was just a quick visit, but I feel like I have so much to say cuz she was just that great. And the PA was also great! An overall great experience, and thank you Tyronique!!",
