        {
          "username": "Tony Campisi",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "101922544482395053334",
          "user_review_count": 8,
          "user_photo_count": 5,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXlpGoTcuypfbp10p56-PqsIY4VqwaqPv_lWZIIIH2y4sBIMdhf=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "My husband and I were on vacation in New York, the Tribeca area. I felt sick and decided to try to find an urgent care. As soon as I walked in to your facility, it was clean and the medical assistant behind the counter was so friendly. She immediately greeted me and was so professional. The paperwork system, which of course was electronic, was very easy.\n\nI was in a room and treated quickly. So much more efficient than where I live in Southern California. everyone was so nice! I was treated with care, respect, and professionalism all while there were smiles on everyone's faces.\n\nI was diagnosed with influenza, type a, given some reassurance that I would be fine, and sent down the block to a CVS for medication's.\n\nI'm back home now, and will remember my positive experience getting really  sick for the first time outside of my home area with high satisfaction for being treated by your medical facility.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SeGVUVkxSazV1YW1GcU9YQnJNMmhRT0daVlRHYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xbb595ac3bf91c4cc!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmRxeTVLRk5uamFqOXBrM2hQOGZVTGc%7C%7C?hl=en",
